
                   get-actor-machine-identifier

Abstract

   get-actor-machine-identifier is a cross-platform JavaScript library
   for generating unique actor machine identifiers.  The software is
   dual-licensed under AGPL-3.0-or-later (for open source use) and a
   commercial license.

